* Desmonus notices the frowns on both of the males faces as they notice that 
she was holding both of their hands, probably each just wanting her for 
themselves. Men, always greedy.
But she could use this fact as well, probably eating her fill without really 
harming either of them...they'de just need a napp for a while.

At first she just thought that Bloodystrike was just going to show her his 
quarters, probably wanting to brage about them. But then she clued in, and 
narrowed her optics a bit.
So, that was what they were both after? Well, she could play this game 
too...making the suffer and wait just a while longer before she fed.

Then noticing the Reptilica also wanted to show her his quarters as well, 
but restraining against both of them the best she could without being 
obviouse.
Though...it was a bit useless, being dragged down the hall by both males, 
each in hope to probably get her to themselves and alone so that they can 
eventually pull off what they had in mind for her.
But that sort of thing barely even made her care, being such a simple thing 
that beings such as these could be pleased with.
Simple pleasures for simple minds.
Feeding upon her pray was where she got her pleasure from, but that would 
all come in time.

However, their arguing was getting tirsome, and she was actually beginning 
to get tired of it.*

" Hmm...maybe a tour isn't best viewed on an empty stomach...perhaps a hot 
drink would be nice...get to know my fellow bots..."

* She gave each of their hands an extra squeeze.*
